Fabricato Surges After Company Says It’s Paid Most of Debts

-- B y   B l a k e   S c h m i d t
-- 
2011-05-20T16:08:32Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-20/fabricato-surges-after-company-says-it-s-paid-most-of-debts.html
Fabricato SA,  Colombia ’s largest
textile maker, soared after the company said it has paid off
most of its debts under a bankruptcy restructuring.  Fabricato rose 6 percent to 53 pesos at 12:06 p.m. New York
time, the highest on a closing basis since June 2007, after
earlier rising as much as 7 percent.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blake Schmidt in Bogota at 
